{"tid":1718871,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"參議院將盡快審議《香港人權與民主法案》，寄望十一月內通過","createTime":"2019-11-14T03:05:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T05:03:44.000Z","uid":134071,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"f89c12553a0e06e82b0a63f0886f3595a9f5223f","tid":1718871,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T03:05:39.000Z","msg":"HKDC係香港人在美國政界遊說組織，有Sharon Hom做顧問<br />\n<br />\n而家，HKDC收到消息：參議院將盡快審議《香港人權與民主法案》，寄望十一月內通過<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://mobile.twitter.com/hkdc_us/status/1194805612108025862\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmobile.twitter.com%2Fhkdc_us%2Fstatus%2F1194805612108025862&d=Ue9aQsdn%2FMYV7LryoIv%2BZDQMt3kYY8c646%2Bk6hbI14w%3D&h=5e31487c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://mobile.twitter.com/hkdc_us/status/1194805612108025862</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WDHtcCM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWDHtcCM.jpg&h=7d8f994a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7d0780f7c3eb93205198df6e79b3dec3c448eea1","tid":1718871,"uid":337761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T03:05:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">連登嘅冷氣軍師，想幫手又冇得發夢嘅，</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔該幫手上Twitter，Reddit幫手！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">前線搏晒老命同班警甴對抗，</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">你哋唔係連撳幾個掣都懶呀嘛？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">Retweet + Like + Reply</span></span><br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n美國議員繼續為香港發聲，大家快啲去回應支持啦～<br />\n<br />\n！！！提出法案嘅Marco Rubio話有好消息！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/marcorubio/status/1194749198345949187?s=09\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmarcorubio%2Fstatus%2F1194749198345949187%3Fs%3D09&d=Ue9aQsdn%2FMYV7LryoIv%2BZDQMt3kYY8c646%2Bk6hbI14w%3